00:30:32.320 --> 00:30:35.190
at least seriously impeded it?

00:30:35.190 --> 00:30:36.490
&gt;&gt; One leader?

00:30:36.490 --> 00:30:37.790
&gt;&gt; Peter Cozzens: Yeah, one leader.

00:30:37.790 --> 00:30:40.910
In the West I think the best chance
would have been before the Civil

00:30:40.910 --> 00:30:49.670
War, would have been maybe in the
