00:30:49.670 --> 00:30:53.720
and I use the term Whites to mean,
you know, non-Native-Americans,

00:30:53.720 --> 00:30:57.730
were crossing the West, were
trying to get to the West coast

00:30:57.730 --> 00:31:00.440
for minerals and for the
Pacific Northwest, for land,

00:31:00.440 --> 00:31:02.200
and we're not settling the West.

00:31:02.200 --> 00:31:03.620
That would have been a time

00:31:03.620 --> 00:31:12.220
when I think sufficient costs could
have been, might have been incurred

00:31:12.220 --> 00:31:18.750
by the government that
negotiations might have led

00:31:18.750 --> 00:31:21.900
to maybe you know one
state, the equivalent

00:31:21.900 --> 00:31:25.320
of one state being set
aside for the Indians.

00:31:25.320 --> 00:31:32.110
But even that would have been a
tall order because you know disease

00:31:32.110 --> 00:31:37.730
and inter-tribal warfare had so
reduced the tribes of the West

00:31:37.730 --> 00:31:43.870 position:56%
that by the time we're talking
about [inaudible] there were no more

00:31:43.870 --> 00:31:48.230
than 200,000 Indians
in the West and again,

00:31:48.230 --> 00:31:52.300
already at least 3 million
Whites and more on the way.

00:31:52.300 --> 00:31:55.980
So, I don't think it was ever,

00:31:55.980 --> 00:31:58.380
ever a realistic possibility
quite honestly in the West

00:31:58.380 --> 00:32:01.600
because the inter-tribal
hatreds were just so great.

00:32:01.600 --> 00:32:04.270
You have a different story
east of the Mississippi.

00:32:04.270 --> 00:32:05.760
I think there was a time when
that could have happened,

00:32:05.760 --> 00:32:09.080
several cases when it could
have happened but not west

00:32:09.080 --> 00:32:11.110
of the Mississippi unfortunately.

