00:32:23.230 --> 00:32:24.530
&gt;&gt; Okay, thank you very much.

00:32:24.530 --> 00:32:25.830
I really enjoyed your talk.

00:32:25.830 --> 00:32:27.130
&gt;&gt; Peter Cozzens: Thank you.

00:32:27.130 --> 00:32:28.430
&gt;&gt; A two-part question, one,
