00:32:31.080 --> 00:32:34.500
to show a lot more
restraint than aggression.

00:32:34.500 --> 00:32:38.200
And I'm interested in that
because they were such a martial,

00:32:38.200 --> 00:32:40.020
I mean if they had a
[inaudible] culture it was

00:32:40.020 --> 00:32:42.140
that they were martial,
particularly on the plains

00:32:42.140 --> 00:32:45.520
and so I'm wondering why you
think that they showed restraint.

00:32:45.520 --> 00:32:47.150
And then the second
