00:32:52.180 --> 00:32:55.950
about what you've reported, but
I'm interested in your conclusions

00:32:55.950 --> 00:32:59.230
about what the appropriate response
is, should we still feel guilty

00:32:59.230 --> 00:33:02.440
as white people here in America or,
what's the appropriate way to look

00:33:02.440 --> 00:33:06.130
on this now in the totality of
everybody had a part to play in it.

00:33:06.130 --> 00:33:09.420 position:56%
&gt;&gt; Peter Cozzens: Okay, well look to
