00:33:09.420 --> 00:33:16.950
interestingly the Indians did
not consider soldiers or Whites

00:33:16.950 --> 00:33:23.850
to be particularly worthy opponents
and in fact they had such contempt

00:33:23.850 --> 00:33:27.790
for soldiers that they would often
scalp them and just toss the scalp

00:33:27.790 --> 00:33:29.090
at the side of the soldier.

00:33:29.090 --> 00:33:32.000
And scalping, a scalp was, you
know an important war honor,

00:33:32.000 --> 00:33:34.580
not the most important but
