00:33:38.970 --> 00:33:43.350 position:56%
And a lot of the, the government had
a very wise and insipid practice of,

00:33:43.350 --> 00:33:46.560
I actually should say,
nefarious military,

00:33:46.560 --> 00:33:49.090
it's whatever word you want to use,
the practice of bringing chiefs

00:33:49.090 --> 00:33:51.700
from the western tribes
to Washington

00:33:51.700 --> 00:33:54.030
and just showing them
