00:33:54.030 --> 00:33:56.170
And you know these chiefs
would come out West, out East

00:33:56.170 --> 00:33:58.100
and they would go back
to their tribe and say,

00:33:58.100 --> 00:34:03.370
my God I've seen giant wigwams,
giant teepees that hold more people

00:34:03.370 --> 00:34:05.060
than we have in our tribes.

00:34:05.060 --> 00:34:09.100
And that all, that tended to have
an effect, a means of kind of like,

00:34:09.100 --> 00:34:13.110
maybe we just can't resist this
and we can't resist this onslaught.

00:34:13.110 --> 00:34:17.720
But it was, I think in large
measure it was the former

00:34:17.720 --> 00:34:21.990
and that they didn't think the
Whites were worthy opponents

00:34:21.990 --> 00:34:25.310
and the culmination of that plus a
lot of them saw the inevitability

00:34:25.310 --> 00:34:27.650
of defeat if they did resist.

00:34:27.650 --> 00:34:31.200
In answer to your second question,

00:34:31.200 --> 00:34:35.080
I mean the answer I'll give will
